<section class="p-4">
  <details>
    <summary class="text-3xl">Hobbies</summary>
    <p class="my-1.5">On my free time, I like contributing to projects that generate positive impacts on the world.</p>

    <div class="flex items-center my-1.5">
      <Cpu class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span>
        At home, I'm a <b>system administrator</b> and <b>network engineer</b>. I manage my own Linux server and <a
