          href="https://www.wireguard.com/">WireGuard</a
        > VPN, along with its own local DNS and NTP servers.</span
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center my-1.5">
      <HandHelping class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span>
        I provide <b>tech support and consulting</b> to friends and family. I assist them in assessing their <b
          >hardware and software</b
        > needs, offering tailored solutions, and implementing them efficiently.</span
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center my-1.5">
      <Book class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span>
        I've <b>written documentation</b> for DiscordChatExporter and CACiC, helping users understand and utilize tools more
        effectively.</span
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center my-1.5">
      <Languages class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span>
        I've volunteered to <b>translate and proofread</b> software projects into <b>Brazilian Portuguese</b> and <b
          >Spanish</b
        >, including platforms such as Discord and MultiMC.</span
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center my-1.5">
      <Palette class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span>
        I am also a <b>graphic designer</b> and <b>UI/UX designer</b>, with experience creating branding, marketing
        materials, accessible interfaces, and various other graphics for multiple projects and events. As an amateur <b
          >3D modeler</b
        >, I enjoy exploring design in three dimensions as well.</span
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center my-1.5">
      <Map class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span>
        I am an active contributor to mapping platforms like Google Maps, where I've made over 1,000 edits, along with
        adding reviews and photos to improve <b>data accuracy</b>. Additionally, I am a Waze map editor and report
        issues to Apple Maps to <b>enhance map quality and user experience</b>.</span
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center my-1.5">
      <Utensils class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span>
        As a food enthusiast, I share my culinary adventures on my reviews blog, where I <b>write experiences</b> about various
        restaurants and dishes.</span
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center my-1.5">
      <Gamepad2 class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span>
        I also enjoy playing video games, reading books, listening to music, <b>studying law</b> and <b></b>preserving
        history.</span
      >
